== 製作 ==
2019年12月，[[Netflix|Netflix]]宣佈將製作韓國電視劇《寧靜海》，該劇改編自崔恆勇導演的2014年同名短篇電影，並由[[鄭雨盛|鄭雨盛]]擔任執行製作人<ref>{{cite web|url=https://about.netflix.com/en/news/netflix-orders-new-korean-sci-fi-thriller-series-the-silent-sea-confirms-actor-jung-woo-sung-as-executive-producer|title=Netflix Orders New Korean Sci-fi Thriller Series The Silent Sea, Confirms Actor Jung Woo-sung As Executive Producer|publisher=[[Netflix|Netflix]]|date=2019-12-22|language=en|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2022-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220106050311/https://about.netflix.com/en/news/netflix-orders-new-korean-sci-fi-thriller-series-the-silent-sea-confirms-actor-jung-woo-sung-as-executive-producer|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年4月，據報導[[孔劉|孔劉]]和[[裴斗娜|裴斗娜]]加入演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|author=吳睿慈|url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/1696545|title=孔劉爆接下Netflix新戲！　劇組8月開拍「卡司超強有他們」|publisher=ETtoday星光雲|date=2020-04-21|language=zh-hant|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105094859/https://star.ettoday.net/news/1696545|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年6月，據報導[[李準_(歌手)|李準]]有望加入演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|author=草莓|url=https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/127595|title=睽違三年！李準有望回歸戲劇，與孔劉、裴斗娜、鄭雨盛合作《寂靜的大海》|publisher=韓星網|date=2020-06-15|language=zh-hant|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107184846/https://www.koreastardaily.com/tc/news/127595|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2020年9月，確認主演陣容<ref>{{cite web|author=蕭采薇|url=https://star.ettoday.net/news/1804128|title=孔劉回歸韓劇「神仙卡司」曝光！　鄭雨盛製作、合體裴斗娜上太空|publisher=ETtoday星光雲|date=2020-09-08|language=zh-hant}}</ref>。同月，宣佈[[許成泰|許成泰]]和[[李茂生_(演員)|李茂生]]加入演員陣容<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sports.donga.com/ent/article/all/20200914/102930009/2|script-title=ko:허성태, 넷플릭스 ‘고요의 바다’ 출연…영화·드라마 열일 행보|publisher=[[東亞日報|東亞日報]]|date=2020-09-14|language=ko|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108205311/https://sports.donga.com/ent/article/all/20200914/102930009/2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mk.co.kr/star/movies/view/2020/09/991487/|script-title=ko:이무생, 정우성 제작 ‘고요의 바다’ 합류…배두나X공유와 호흡[공식]|publisher=StarToday|date=2020-09-25|language=ko|access-date=2020-11-01|archive-date=2020-11-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105072530/https://www.mk.co.kr/star/movies/view/2020/09/991487/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

